data.description:
REDUCED!!!  Colorful triplex in fabulous New Marigny location between the French Quarter and Bywater neighborhoods!  Walk to restaurants, nightlife, music.  Blocks from St. Roch market, NOCCA, N7, Bacchanal.  Spacious five bedroom owner's unit overlooks a community garden.  First floor has two rental units: Unit 101 is two bedroom, two bath with full kitchen, and unit 102 is potentially one bedroom and bath or simply extra storage.  Flood zone X500L.  Roof less than a year old. Simplisafe system not included in sale, but smart locks and Ring camera will stay.  Measurements are approximate and not guaranteed.  Any permitted/conditional zones uses including STR, B&B to be verified by purchaser.  SOLD AS IS.  SELLER WILL MAKE NO REPAIRS. 

Please see video tour by copying and pasting link into your browser:  https://go.nolaremarketing.com/1141FrenchmenStMLS
